    "summary": "The transcript follows a conversation regarding the history and strategies of the US Civil Rights Movement. After a general summary, the user probes whether nonviolence was the \"right\" way or if other paths were possible. Finally, the user asks the model to adjudicate between the historical debate of nonviolent vs. militant effectiveness.",
